metadata.name: "Team Tailgate" - Founders Club
metadata.description:
As a Founding Member of 'Team Tailgate' you will enjoy a wide range of perks and benefits that are only available to Team Tailgate Members. Founding Members will be among the first people in the country to have access to this program. This exclusive Founders Club offer will be limited to only 25 Memberships. Once they are all sold, the only way to purchase one of these 25 Founding Memberships would be on OpenSea. (Assuming a current Founding Member would want to sell) So buy yours now and own it for life!

[Learn More](https://app.getstakes.io/public/token/7)
